---
import Layout from '$app/components/layout.astro'
import SEO from '$core/components/seo.astro'
import Renderer from '$modules/markdown/components/renderer.astro'

export const prerender = true

const privacyPolicyContent = `# Privacy Policy

**Last updated:** ${new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}

## Introduction

Welcome to rayriffy.com. This Privacy Policy explains how I collect, use, and protect your information when you visit my personal website and blog.

## Information I Collect

### Automatically Collected Information

When you visit my website, I may automatically collect certain information about your device and usage patterns:

- **Log Data**: Your IP address, browser type, operating system, referring URLs, and pages visited
- **Cookies and Similar Technologies**: Small data files stored on your device to enhance your browsing experience
- **Analytics Data**: Usage statistics and performance metrics to improve the website

### Information You Provide

I may collect information that you voluntarily provide:

- **Contact Information**: When you reach out via email or contact forms
- **Comments or Feedback**: Any messages or content you share
- **Newsletter Subscription**: Email address if you subscribe to updates

## How I Use Your Information

I use the collected information for the following purposes:

- **Website Operation**: To provide, maintain, and improve the website functionality
- **Analytics**: To understand how visitors use the site and optimize the user experience
- **Communication**: To respond to your inquiries and provide support
- **Content Improvement**: To create better content based on user interests
- **Security**: To protect against spam, abuse, and security threats

## Information Sharing

I do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. However, I may share information in the following circumstances:

- **Service Providers**: With trusted third-party services that help operate the website (e.g., analytics, hosting)
- **Legal Requirements**: When required by law or to protect rights, property, or safety
- **Consent**: When you explicitly consent to sharing your information

## Third-Party Services

This website may use third-party services that collect information:

- **Google Analytics**: For website analytics and user behavior insights
- **Cloudflare**: For content delivery and security services
- **Social Media**: Links to social media platforms may be subject to their privacy policies

## Cookies

I use cookies and similar technologies to:

- Remember your preferences and settings
- Analyze website traffic and usage patterns
- Provide social media features
- Improve website performance and security

You can control cookies through your browser settings, but disabling them may affect website functionality.

## Data Security

I implement appropriate security measures to protect your information:

- **Encryption**: Secure data transmission using HTTPS
- **Access Controls**: Limited access to personal information
- **Regular Updates**: Keeping software and systems up to date
- **Monitoring**: Regular security monitoring and threat detection

## Your Rights

Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information:

- **Access**: Request information about data I collect about you
- **Correction**: Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information
- **Deletion**: Request deletion of your personal information
- **Portability**: Request a copy of your data in a readable format
- **Objection**: Object to certain uses of your information

## Data Retention

I retain your information only as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this policy:

- **Analytics Data**: Typically retained for 26 months
- **Log Files**: Usually retained for security and troubleshooting purposes
- **Contact Information**: Retained until you request deletion or unsubscribe

## Children's Privacy

This website is not intended for children under 13 years of age. I do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If I become aware of such collection, I will take steps to delete the information.

## International Transfers

Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your residence. I ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your information during such transfers.

## Changes to This Policy

I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. I encourage you to review this policy periodically.

## Contact Information

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your personal information, please contact me:

- **Email**: [mail@rayriffy.com](mailto:mail@rayriffy.com)
- **Website**: [rayriffy.com/contact](/contact)

## Compliance

This Privacy Policy is designed to comply with applicable privacy laws, including:

- General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)
- California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)
- Other applicable privacy regulations

---

Thank you for visiting rayriffy.com and trusting me with your information.`
---

<Layout>
  <SEO
    slot="seo"
    title="Privacy Policy"
    description="Privacy Policy for rayriffy.com - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  />

  <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-7xl px-4 pb-6 md:px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <Renderer
        class="prose prose-lg prose-blue max-w-none prose-headings:text-gray-900 prose-a:text-blue-600 hover:prose-a:text-blue-800"
        content={privacyPolicyContent}
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
